title: Hokkaido Sapporo Higashi High School
data: Hokkaido Sapporo Higashi High School (北海道札幌東高等学校, Hokkaidō Sapporo Higashi Kōtō Gakkō) is a high school in Sapporo, Hokkaido, Japan, founded in 1907. Hokkaido Sapporo Higashi High School is one of high schools administered by Hokkaido.
